data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. BRAND NEW EXTERIOR COLOR!! You'll fall in love with this expansive high ceilinged 3-bedroom, 2-bath home in Bartow. Boasting 1880 sq ft of heated living space and a grand total of 2472 sq ft under the 2018 roof, this spacious property is a true gem. Step inside through the massive double front doors to experience the openness of the high ceilings and the warmth of a well-designed layout. Your family will love the vibrant and cheerful kitchen, featuring a glass cooktop and a convection oven - a culinary enthusiast's dream. A separate dining room, living room, and family room provide oodles of space for gatherings and daily life. Embrace the lovely weather with a screened porch adorned with pavers and a built-in storage bench – perfect for enjoying the sunny days. Beyond the screen, a large paver pad extends the entertainment space into the open air. The expansive fenced backyard invites endless possibilities, create a play space or add a water feature for a zen garden feeling. Park with ease in the large 2-car garage, providing additional storage space and a work bench. This home is designed for both comfort and practicality. Situated in a desirable location, this property offers the perfect combination of tranquility and accessibility to schools, multiple parks, and local amenities like the library, civic center and sports park. Seize the opportunity to call this house your home. Schedule a viewing today to explore the countless features and possibilities that await you!
